and I was like, "Wait, large size? Regular size?"

1268
01:10:44,912 --> 01:10:47,912
Big cat means big acrylic!

1269
01:10:47,912 --> 01:10:51,712
Oh yeah, that's what happened though! Big acrylic!

1270
01:10:51,712 --> 01:10:54,012
Large size!

1271
01:10:54,012 --> 01:10:58,312
In fact, Justice is coming to life as 3D acrylic stands!

1272
01:10:58,312 --> 01:11:02,412
Everyone loves acrylic stands, right? I love them!

1273
01:11:02,412 --> 01:11:06,412
Whether you have a room dedicated to acrylic stands or just starting your collection,

1274
01:11:06,412 --> 01:11:10,112
you are going to need all of Justice, okay?

1275
01:11:10,112 --> 01:11:11,812
Get them all! Yes!

1276
01:11:11,812 --> 01:11:14,712
All of them! Whoo!

1277
01:11:14,712 --> 01:11:17,412
Next one. Oh, it's me! Ha ha!

1278
01:11:17,412 --> 01:11:20,712
Okay! Whoo!

1279
01:11:20,712 --> 01:11:23,712
And as we all mentioned during our 3D showcases,

1280
01:11:23,712 --> 01:11:27,512
we each have our own merch too. Oh la la!

1281
01:11:27,512 --> 01:11:30,412
All right then, I will start!

1282
01:11:30,412 --> 01:11:32,512
Ha ha ha!

1283
01:11:32,512 --> 01:11:36,112
This right here is the paper knife and acrylic stand!

1284
01:11:36,112 --> 01:11:40,512
It's a lovely set inspired by the design of my sword, Thorn!

1285
01:11:40,512 --> 01:11:43,812
Yeah! Whoo!

1286
01:11:43,812 --> 01:11:47,412
This paper knife can actually be displayed by resting it on the acrylic stand!

1287
01:11:47,412 --> 01:11:50,612
It's so cool! You all get your own Thorn!

1288
01:11:50,612 --> 01:11:54,112
No, no! Baby Thorn!

1289
01:11:54,112 --> 01:11:57,712
Baby Thorn! So cute!

1290
01:11:57,712 --> 01:12:02,412
Oh gosh, I can't... I can't! Oh, it's so cool!

1291
01:12:02,412 --> 01:12:04,612
Gigi, you go, you go, you go!

1292
01:12:04,612 --> 01:12:07,612
Ha ha ha!

1293
01:12:07,612 --> 01:12:11,512
And now, a hand-in cushion for Otomo!

1294
01:12:11,512 --> 01:12:14,112
Do you remember seeing it?

1295
01:12:14,112 --> 01:12:17,612
Sadly, there is no Oji-san to show you how soft and fluffy it is,

1296
01:12:17,612 --> 01:12:21,112
but it is very fluffy and it's made from a very squishy material!

1297
01:12:21,112 --> 01:12:25,112
You'll never want to stop squeezing it!

1298
01:12:25,112 --> 01:12:29,112
I'm going to squeeze it! It's so cute!

1299
01:12:29,112 --> 01:12:32,612
And it's a hand! Yay!

1300
01:12:32,612 --> 01:12:36,412
Cici! Whoa! Cici!

1301
01:12:36,412 --> 01:12:39,712
Check this out!

1302
01:12:39,712 --> 01:12:42,612
It's a Tomo pouch and sock set!

1303
01:12:42,612 --> 01:12:47,112
Do you want the socks? Monday, Tuesday, every day of the week, seven pairs of socks!

1304
01:12:47,112 --> 01:12:51,312
And then you have your little pouch, the little Tomo pouch to put them in. It's so cute!

1305
01:12:51,312 --> 01:12:54,312
It's really cute, you can put anything in it, of course, not only socks.

1306
01:12:54,312 --> 01:12:57,612
But I really like it. It reminds me of the Otomo pouch I made once.

1307
01:12:57,612 --> 01:13:02,112
I like it a lot! Yay! Please get it! Yay!

1308
01:13:02,112 --> 01:13:05,112
Okay, Raora!

1309
01:13:05,112 --> 01:13:07,912
You could put your toes in your Otomo socks!

1310
01:13:07,912 --> 01:13:09,612
Ha ha! It's my turn!

1311
01:13:09,612 --> 01:13:13,512
And this is Raora's pencil case and keychain set!

1312
01:13:13,512 --> 01:13:18,112
It's me wearing a Tattino costume, and ah, I'd be so happy if you fill it... so cute!

1313
01:13:18,112 --> 01:13:22,112
You like it? Yeah!

1314
01:13:22,112 --> 01:13:25,912
I'd be so happy if you fill it with stationery and use it at school or in the office,

1315
01:13:25,912 --> 01:13:31,112
or really anywhere you want!

1316
01:13:31,112 --> 01:13:34,112
And the keychain can be attached to the pencil case,

1317
01:13:34,112 --> 01:13:38,312
so you clip it to your bag or anything you like!

1318
01:13:38,312 --> 01:13:41,112
Super cute! Yay!

1319
01:13:41,112 --> 01:13:44,312
Everything's really cute! I'm super excited to see you guys!

1320
01:13:44,312 --> 01:13:48,112
I'm so excited to see all of Justice's merch!

1321
01:13:48,112 --> 01:13:51,112
And if you want to know when can we purchase them?

1322
01:13:51,112 --> 01:13:54,112
Well, they will all be available to purchase right after this stream!

1323
01:13:54,112 --> 01:13:56,612
So make sure to get them ASAP! ASAP!

1324
01:13:56,612 --> 01:13:59,112
And that's our merch announcement! Yeah!

1325
01:13:59,112 --> 01:14:02,612
That's the first one, and...

1326
01:14:02,612 --> 01:14:05,612
And as Cici just mentioned, there is one more announcement!

1327
01:14:05,612 --> 01:14:09,712
And you all know Justice will be performing live for the very first time...

1328
01:14:09,712 --> 01:14:14,112
at the Hololive English 3rd Concert! Oh my god!

1329
01:14:14,112 --> 01:14:18,612
Taking place at the Radio City Music Hall in New York on August 23rd and 24th PDT!

1330
01:14:18,612 --> 01:14:22,112
And right after this stream...

1331
01:14:22,112 --> 01:14:25,612
we will be redirecting you into the music video, "All For One"!

1332
01:14:25,612 --> 01:14:29,112
Justice is also in there, of course!

1333
01:14:29,112 --> 01:14:32,512
And maybe you'll see us doing some stuff! Who knows?

1334
01:14:32,512 --> 01:14:35,112
We'll be moving and grooving! Maybe!

1335
01:14:35,112 --> 01:14:39,112
So make sure to stay tuned! It's going to be very, very soon!

1336
01:14:39,112 --> 01:14:42,112
Gosh, all right everyone! Oh gosh!

1337
01:15:00,120 --> 01:15:02,253
It's getting a little sad,

1338
01:15:02,253 --> 01:15:05,120
but it's almost time to say goodbye.

1339
01:15:05,253 --> 01:15:09,720
But before we go, let's each share our thoughts and thank all our fans for their support.

1340
01:15:09,720 --> 01:15:11,920
Uh, Gigi, you go first.

1341
01:15:11,920 --> 01:15:13,720
Me? Me? Okay!

1342
01:15:13,720 --> 01:15:18,020
Grambs, thank you so much for supporting us all this time!

1343
01:15:18,120 --> 01:15:21,920
And can you believe it's been a little over a year now?

1344
01:15:21,986 --> 01:15:25,620
And so many more years with Justiciates, Justice, and Grambs! Yay!

1345
01:15:29,620 --> 01:15:32,520
Gosh, we... Hello!

1346
01:15:32,520 --> 01:15:35,420
Thank you so much!

1347
01:15:35,453 --> 01:15:38,720
Gosh, Rosarians, give me a mighty huzzah!

1348
01:15:38,786 --> 01:15:41,620
We did it! Oh my gosh, thank you so much for joining all of us on our adventure here at Holo!

1349
01:15:41,653 --> 01:15:44,920
I can't... I can't believe it! Oh my gosh, we're 3D now!

1350
01:15:44,920 --> 01:15:49,120
And we're going to be in a concert, and... oh... everything's happening!

1351
01:15:49,120 --> 01:15:54,020
Like all our dreams are coming true, and it's all thanks to you guys!

1352
01:15:54,120 --> 01:15:56,920
Thank you so, so much!

1353
01:15:56,986 --> 01:16:02,420
Onwards and upwards! Huzzah!

1354
01:16:02,453 --> 01:16:05,120
Thank you very much! Thank you so much, everyone!

1355
01:16:05,120 --> 01:16:07,520
Thank you Justiciates! Thank you Toto! Thank you everyone!

1356
01:16:07,520 --> 01:16:09,220
Thank you Justice, of course!

1357
01:16:09,253 --> 01:16:13,520
It's been a lot of fun, we worked very hard, and I'm so excited and happy that you all got to see it finally!

1358
01:16:13,520 --> 01:16:16,920
And we're also really excited to be in the EN 3D concert, so yeah!

1359
01:16:16,920 --> 01:16:21,120
Thank you from the bottom of our heart for supporting us thus far!

1360
01:16:21,120 --> 01:16:25,620
Please keep supporting us for much, much longer! Thank you!

1361
01:16:25,653 --> 01:16:29,520
Ciao, Totini! Sora, Tora, Tat!

1362
01:16:29,520 --> 01:16:35,920
Thank you so much for supporting Justice for a whole year and many more to come!

1363
01:16:35,920 --> 01:16:40,620
This... this has been a dream come true for me, being in 3D, dancing with you guys!

1364
01:16:40,620 --> 01:16:46,420
So much fun, so I really, really appreciate it.

1365
01:16:46,486 --> 01:16:50,220
Thank you so much from the bottom of my heart.

1366
01:16:50,286 --> 01:16:55,820
Big Cat Means Big Justice! With Justice! Way!

1367
01:16:55,853 --> 01:17:00,020
Once again, thank you all for watching our very first 3D collab stream today!

1368
01:17:00,020 --> 01:17:02,920
Please keep supporting Justice!

1369
01:17:02,920 --> 01:17:05,620
Justice! Just like that!

1370
01:17:05,620 --> 01:17:08,620
Justice! Get, get, get!

1371
01:17:08,620 --> 01:17:11,920
Justice!

1372
01:17:11,920 --> 01:17:16,120
Bye-bye everyone!

1373
01:17:22,120 --> 01:17:25,620
Make sure to eat-y noms, hydrate, and all that jazz!

1374
01:17:25,620 --> 01:17:29,620
All right, bye!

